  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      602.59,
      526.72,
      634.21
    ],
    "text": "Clarification Regarding a Social Media News Report on an Incident at the Colombo District Crime Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      648.79,
      526.7,
      712.57
    ],
    "text": "A news report is currently circulating across social media platforms alleging that a birthday celebration, including a cake-cutting event, was held at the Colombo District Crime Division (CCD) on 29.03.2026 for the suspect Ishara Sewwandi, who is presently held under detention orders.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      727.15,
      526.4,
      807.15
    ],
    "text": "As it has been observed that misleading and inaccurate information is also being disseminated in relation to this alleged incident, measures have been taken to obtain a comprehensive report from the Deputy Inspector General of Police in charge of the Colombo District. Based on the findings of that report, the following clarification is issued.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      32.13,
      526.77,
      95.93
    ],
    "text": "The DIG in charge of the Colombo District has stated that intelligence was received regarding a plan to organize a birthday cake-cutting event for the aforementioned suspect. Accordingly, prompt action was taken to prevent the occurrence of such an activity.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      110.51,
      526.93,
      174.29
    ],
    "text": "As an initial administrative measure, the Officer-in-Charge (OIC) of the Colombo District Crime Division has been transferred to the Police Field Force Headquarters with immediate effect, under the directive of the Inspector General of Police (IGP).",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      188.87,
      526.68,
      284.96
    ],
    "text": "While all police personnel are required to uphold the highest standards of professional conduct and ethical responsibility, a special inquiry has been launched by the Criminal Investigation Department (CID) together with the Police Special Investigation Unit, under the instructions of the IGP, to investigate the alleged misconduct and unlawful actions of the officers concerned.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      299.54,
      205.4,
      315.08
    ],
    "text": "Police Media Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  }
